[http://gphoto.sourceforge.net/ '''gphoto'''] is a set of tools and libraries not just for retrieving images from cameras, but also to upload and remote control the configuration of your camera (if supported by the camera).

== Installation ==
Install GPhoto2:
{{Emerge|media-gfx/gphoto2}}

== Getting started ==
To import images from your camera, plug your camera in, go to the directory you want to import the images to, and use gphoto:
{{Cmd|gphoto2 -p }}

